Package: epicseg
Type: Package
Title: Chromatin Segmentation in R
Version: 1.0
Date: 2014-12-05
Author: Alessandro Mammana
Maintainer: Alessandro Mammana <mammana@molgen.mpg.de>
Description: This package computes a segmentation of the genome and a
    probabilistic model based on count data from histone marks (or other NGS
    experiments).
License: GPL-2
SystemRequirements: C++11 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: 
    parallel,
    RColorBrewer,
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.3),
    IRanges,
    GenomicRanges,
    kfoots,
    bamsignals,
    edgeR
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: testthat
